# AI-Guided Self-Reflection Session Platform — System Architecture

## 1. Executive Summary

An AI-guided self-reflection platform where a **Simli avatar** acts as a compassionate listener, guiding users through structured question scripts. The AI **never gives advice or opinions** — it follows pre-defined scripts, analyzes user sentiment, and manages the session flow. All session data is stored for doctor/clinician review.

---

## 2. Core Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Frontend — Next.js / React"
        U[User with Microphone] -->|Audio Stream| WR[WebRTC Transport]
        WR -->|Avatar Video + Audio| AV[Simli Avatar Display]
        AV --> U
        UI[Session UI] --> SS[Session Status Panel]
    end

    subgraph "Real-Time Pipeline — Pipecat Server"
        WR <-->|WebRTC| PC[Pipecat Pipeline]
        PC --> STT[Deepgram STT<br/>Real-time Streaming]
        STT --> CA[Context Aggregator]
        CA --> LLM[LLM Brain<br/>via LangChain]
        LLM --> TTS[ElevenLabs / Cartesia TTS]
        TTS --> SIM[Simli Video Service]
        SIM --> PC
    end

    subgraph "Backend — FastAPI"
        LLM <-->|REST/WebSocket| API[FastAPI Server]
        API --> SM[Script Manager]
        API --> SA[Sentiment Analyzer]
        API --> SH[Session Handler]
        SH --> DB[(PostgreSQL)]
    end

    subgraph "Doctor Dashboard"
        DB --> DD[Doctor Portal<br/>Session Transcripts & Analytics]
    end
```

